Module jakarta.nosql.communication.column
Package jakarta.nosql.column

Interface ColumnConfiguration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Function<Settings,​ColumnManagerFactory>
    public interface ColumnConfiguration
extends Function<Settings,​ColumnManagerFactory>
    It is a function that reads from Settings and then creates a manager factory instance. It should return a NullPointerException when the Settings parameter is null.
    See Also:
    ColumnManagerFactory, ColumnManager
